--------------------------------------------------------
|0 |DISTRIBUTED DELETE      |    |1       |23          |
|1 |└─HASH RIGHT OUTER JOIN |    |1       |5           |
|2 |  ├─TABLE FULL SCAN     |t2  |1       |3           |
|3 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN     |tt1 |1       |3           |
